<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.11">
<l>āyaṉuk kākattāṉ kaṇṭa kaṉāviṉai</l>
<l>vēyar pukaḻvilli puttūrkkōṉ kōtaicol</l>
<l>tūya tamiḻmālai yīraintum vallavar</l>
<l>vāyunaṉ makkaḷaip peṟṟu makiḻvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those capable [of reciting]</l>
<l rend="indent">all ten [songs from] the pure Tamil garland,</l>
<l rend="indent">uttered by Kōtai, [daughter of] the lord of Villiputtūr praised by the brahmins,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the dream that she had of becoming the Cowherd's [wife],</l>
<l> shall rejoice begetting exceedingly good children.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
